Class Sprite

  • java.lang.Object
    • Sprite
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Sprite>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroundSprite, Moveable

    public abstract class Sprite
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Sprite>
    The Sprite abstract class represents a simple displayable rectangle object with supporting methods to get information about the object
    Version:
    May 16, 2018
    Author:
    Roshan Sevalia, Period: 4, Assignment: APCSfinal, Sources: Charlie Huang, Gaurav Vipat
